          <p><b>Booking Methods:</b></br>At Road Runners, we offer convenient and easy-to-use booking options to suit your needs.</br> You can book your tickets through any of the following methods:</br>Online Booking: You can book your tickets online through our website or mobile app. Our online booking system is fast, secure, and easy to use. You can choose your seat, make payment, and receive your e-ticket in just a few clicks.</br>Phone Booking: If you prefer to book your tickets over the phone, our customer support team is available 24/7 to assist you. Simply call our booking hotline and provide your travel details, and our agents will guide you through the booking process and help you secure your seats.</br>In-person Booking: For those who prefer to book their tickets in person, you can visit any of our ticketing offices located in major cities across the country. Our friendly staff will be happy to assist you with your booking and answer any questions you may have about our services.</br>No matter which booking method you choose, we guarantee a hassle-free and enjoyable booking experience. So why wait? Book your tickets with Road Runners today and experience the best in bus travel.</br></br>
